  "texts": [
    "That is, we assume that we can access a sample of pairs object-label, that we will call the data, or the observations: (X 1, Y 1),.",
    ", (X n, Y n).",
    "From now, and until the end of Section 4, we assume that (X 1, Y 1),.",
    ", (X n, Y n) are i.i.d. from P.",
    "That is, they are \"typical examples\" of the pairs object-label the machine will have to deal with in the future."
  ]
